dp-admin
===========

dP Directory - Admin Portal

1. Checkout code from github.
2. Change curent folder to dp-admin.
3. Install node.js <b>sudo apt-get install nodejs</b>
4. Install npm <b>sudo apt-get install npm</b>
5. Install bower <b>sudo npm install -g bower</b> ( Check bower version for verification - <b>bower -version</b> )
6. Run <b> bower install </b>. This will download all the dependencies.
7. In nginx, point to the absolute path of dp-admin/app. 
